<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Sofia' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Turtle Shelter Project</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .landing-image img {
            width: 100%;
            filter: brightness(0.6);
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .overlay button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #228B22;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .overlay button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .cards {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .card a {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #228B22;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .card a:hover {
            background-color: #1a681a;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #228B22;
            color: white;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Landing Image -->
    <div class="landing-image">
        <picture>
            <source srcset="/images/landingpagemobile.jpeg" media="(max-width: 768px)">
            <img src="/images/landingpage.png" alt="Landing Page Image">
        </picture>
        <div class="overlay">
            <h1>Saving the lives of people battling homelessness</h1>
            <h1 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 2.5rem;">BEGINS WITH YOU</h1>
            <div>
                <a href="/about-us"><button>About Us</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Our Mission -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            What is a turtle shelter vest? a high tech but simple solution to help save lives -
a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle...

        </p>
        <p>and YOU can help!  </p>
        <br>
        <p>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death.  </p>

    <p>Jen is no longer homeless and has figured out a solution:</p>
<p> High tech foam vests that are inexpensive,
            keep a person warm to 10 degree below zero, help SAVE lives and alleviate suffering.</p>
        <p>
            YOU can request vests for your community - and you can make vests and have your friends, business colleagues, church members or club make vests, too! </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Section: How You Can Help -->
    <section class="section">
        <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/vvvest.jpg" alt="volunteer" style="width: 700px; height: auto; border-radius: 10px;">
                <h3 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 2.5 rem;">Volunteer</h3>
                <p>Join our team of dedicated volunteers and help us provide essential services.</p>
                <a href="/volunteer">Learn More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/vvest.jpg" alt="donate" style="width: 700px; height: auto; border-radius: 10px;">
                <h3 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 2.5 rem;">Donate</h3>
                <p>Your donations directly support our programs and services.</p>
                <a href="/donate">Donate Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/sewing.jpg" alt="sewing" style="width: 700px; height: auto; border-radius: 10px;">
                <h3 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 2.5 rem;">Host an Event</h3>
                <p>Partner with us to host an event that helps our community.</p>
                <a href="/request-an-event">Request Event</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section: Recent Updates -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;">
        <h2>Recent Updates</h2>
        <p>Stay tuned for our latest events, stories, and updates from the field.</p>
        <a href="/upcoming-events" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #228B22;">View Upcoming Events</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>TURTLE SHELTER PROJECT, PO BOX 382, KAYSVILLE, UT 84037 | 801-872-3190 | 
            <a href="mailto:turtleshelterproject@gmail.com">turtleshelterproject@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <div>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/turtleshelterproject/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/turtleshelterproject/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@turtleshelterproject7915/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
